name: One tree. One planet.
description:
For every NFT sold, I will plant trees with at least half of the proceeds. I will be partnering with One Tree Planted to help with global reforestation efforts. One dollar. One tree. One planet.

she wanted
everyone.
bare black fingers
thrust out to touch
his tendrils of spring.
he flows on bluejay wings.
leaving her palms cold, empty,
and grasping brutal wind
drops dreaming of
leaves, sun, and evergreen
family forests.
_ V

"This oak tree and me, we're made of the same stuff." Carl Sagan
